    <item>
      <title>内格尔表示，如果数据证实其预测，欧洲央行可能会降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/ecb-can-cut-rates-if-data-confirm-economic-forecast-nagel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员约阿希姆·内格尔表示，如果新的预测和新数据证实消费者价格增速将回升至 2%，欧洲央行可能会降低借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/ecb-can-cut-rates-if-data-confirm-economic-forecast-nagel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行在降息时机上存在分歧，药丸中的鹰派语气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/boe-chief-economist-says-uk-is-getting-closer-to-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行的利率制定者对于基准贷款利率下调的时机似乎越来越分歧，首席经济学家休·皮尔(Huw Pill)加入鹰派行列，对持续存在的通胀表示谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/boe-chief-economist-says-uk-is-getting-closer-to-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:24:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
